metadata.name: Afarin
metadata.description:
The feelings of women have always been linked to their desire for nature, in the place where women's duties lose their meaning, they talked to nature about their inner thoughts.
Women have always had nature as the audience for their unrestricted and free words.
 My collection has been heavily influenced by this statement.

Digital painting

Edition 1/1
Image size - 4286 x 6000
